Titolo: Rocky Super Action Boxing

Anno: 1983

Descrizione: Rocky Super Action Boxing is the first licensed video game based on the Rocky franchise. The game is based on Rocky III and was designed by Coleco for its ColecoVision console. The player can play as either Rocky Balboa or Clubber Lang, either against the computer in a one player game, or against each other in a "Head to Head" two player mode. There is also a "Demo" mode if the player wants to watch Rocky and Clubber Lang fight.

Genere: Fighting 

Valutazione: N/A
